author: DAVE SKRETTA
title: Baylor quarterback Russell finally gets to play at Kansas
text:
Baylor quarterback Russell finally gets to play at Kansas Associated Press | 0 comments 
LAWRENCE, Kan. (AP) — Rather than playing for one of the best teams in major college football, quarterback Seth Russell was oh-so-close to playing for what is arguably the worst. 
The talented junior from the Dallas area was recruited by Kansas coach Turner Gill, and for a while had committed there.
